longBusinessSummary: Dios Exploration Inc. engages in the exploration and evaluation of mineral resource properties in Canada. The company explores for gold, diamond, copper, and silver deposits. Its projects include AU33, a gold research project covering 87 square kilometers; CLARKIE, a 100% owned project located Near Eastmain Clearwater gold deposit and Eleonore Newmont gold mine; K2, a 100% owned gold research project with 162 claims covering 82 square kilometers along the Opinaca River; and 33 CARATS, a gold and diamond research project located on the east side of the Eastmain River. The company is based in Montreal, Canada.
